{"tid":877470,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"3星 Galaxy S10 系列將針對 iPhone XR 及 XS","createTime":"2018-10-26T11:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T15:05:08.000Z","uid":109383,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8efb19cf1d6846286f4f8ba2e11faf8ca5094d","tid":877470,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"Samsung 跟 Apple 在智能電話方面一直是死對頭的關係，Samsung 的產品基本上都是看著 iPhone 作競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n今次再有消息指 Samsung 明年推出的Galaxy S10 系列，或與 Apple 今年發售的年度產品 iPhone XR、XS 及 XS Max 作正面的挑戰。根據消息指，明年 Samsung 也會為 Galaxy S10 系列推出三個款式。當中分別是 SM-G970x、SM-G973x 及 SM-G975X。<br />\n<br />\n有指 SM-G970x (Galaxy S10 Lite)、SM-G973x (Galaxy S10) 及 SM-G975X (Galaxy S10 Plus) 的假想敵分別為 iPhone XR、iPhone XS 及 iPhone XS Max。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/190955_7903d65f9c7ebd326b59fd9b8a0cdb85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F190955_7903d65f9c7ebd326b59fd9b8a0cdb85.png&h=bf16ad76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多年來，兩家公司在智慧手機市場展開了激烈競爭，甚至多次將對方告上了法庭。在蘋果推出 iPhone XR / Xs / Xs Max 三條產品線後，傳聞稱三星也為 Galaxy S10 制定了類似的計畫，其中入門機型（SM-G970x）的存儲容量為。代號為 SM-G975x 的機型，據說是 Galaxy S10 系列的旗艦，它將與 iPhone Xs Max 展開對抗。雖然還不能 100% 確定它叫啥，但有一點可以保證的 &mdash;&mdash; 它的體型會非常大。<br />\n<br />\n站在中間的 SM-G973x 機型（S10 標準版），將和 S10 Plus 一樣從 128GB ROM 起跳，同時可選 256 / 512GB 存儲容量（甚至支援 UFS 3.0）。<br />\n<br />\n傳聞 Galaxy S10 系列有關規格資料為：<br />\n<br />\nLite：5.8 英寸、平面屏、側邊指紋感應、支援 4G 網路、64GB ROM 起跳；<br />\n<br />\nS10：5.8 英寸、弧面屏、屏幕下指紋識別、支援 5G 網路、128GB ROM 起跳，還有 256GB 及 512GB ROM 版 (甚至支援 UFS 3.0)<br />\n<br />\nS10 Plus：6.4 英寸、弧面屏、屏幕下指紋識別、支援 5G 網路，跟 S10 一樣 128GB ROM 起跳，還有 256GB 及 512GB ROM 版 (甚至支援 UFS 3.0)<br />\n<br />\n而價格方面，傳聞 Galaxy S10 Lite 與 iPhone XR 相同，約為 750 美元；Galaxy S10 接近 1 萬港元，S10 Plus 更可能接近 1.1 萬港元；<br />\n<br />\n外界 Samsung 將於 2019 年 2 月 24 日發佈 Galaxy S10，並於發佈一個星期後正式發售。<br />\n<br />\n3星唔會跟住做咁傻仔啊？ 本身已經有s s+ note...."},{"pid":"f1c9bdb735c61def769254e95311595060bb3a75","tid":877470,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"我想要平mon samsung旗艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567dd049d6a4d9f1c60a691a42b038e96205d016","tid":877470,"uid":196075,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"samsung機賣1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5d9e64e91129225bee573f5323de111eca5f6c","tid":877470,"uid":109383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f1c9bdb735c61def769254e95311595060bb3a75","tid":877470,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"我想要平mon samsung旗艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"終於有平面機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過學an俠咁講S10 lite (XR)係低階機"},{"pid":"84b441d500a22d3af0f975bf3f41f28ac7bf5e41","tid":877470,"uid":56604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"出部s10 plus 同note 系列要幾大部先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6023405450ebfd4df617b549735c3260e0d95662","tid":877470,"uid":85557,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"567dd049d6a4d9f1c60a691a42b038e96205d016","tid":877470,"uid":196075,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"samsung機賣1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T11:22:26.000Z","msg":"D硬件咁垃圾都收咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal